Sheila Marriot, 80, has already contributed to two Guinness World Records for handmade blankets. Now, this Port Elizabeth granny is working towards a third record the World s Largest Portrait Blanket, made under the auspices of the 67 Blankets for Nelson Mandela Day &#8211; and she s teaching the children in her complex a skill in the process. Related Share on Facebook Share Share on Twitter Tweet Share on Google Plus Share